		  factor F is to simulate gravitational instability with
		  B_eff_ ~ 0.5(F - 1). Nevertheless, with datasets of
		  sufficient size it is possible to distinguish the two
		  effects, We discuss in detail how this should be done, and
		  give a maximum-likelihood method for extracting {LAMBDA}
		  and betab from anisotropic power-spectrum data.
