		  are accurately predicted for the velocity divergence. In
		  contrast, the theoretical values for the density bias
		  parameters do not accurately match the numerical results as
		  a function of halo mass. This is likely due to the
		  simplistic assumptions that relate virialized haloes to
		  density peaks of a given height in the model. We also
