		  star formation. In both hydrodynamic simulations, the
		  clustering of the gas is suppressed while that of dark
		  matter is boosted at scales k>1 h Mpc-1. Despite this
		  counterbalance between dark matter and gas, the clustering
		  of the total matter is suppressed by up to 1% at 1 h
		  Mpc-1<~k<~10 h Mpc-1, while for k~20 h Mpc-1 it is boosted,
