		  halo and mass density contrasts from the extended
		  Press-Schechter theory. Since this function is derived in
		  the framework of the standard gravitational instability
		  theory assuming the random Gaussianity of the primordial
		  density field alone, we expect that the basic features of
		  the nonlinear and stochastic biasing predicted from our
